OL,3,CCriminal barristers to strike
OL,4,Cindefinitely over justice system
OL,5,C'crisis'
OL,7,FCriminal barristers in Northern
OL,8,FIreland who are striking indefinitely
OL,9,Ffrom Monday have called for urgency in
OL,10,Faddressing the "crisis" in the justice
OL,11,Fsystem.
OL,13,FDonal Lunny KC, chairman of the Bar
OL,14,FCouncil of Northern Ireland, said
OL,15,Fbarristers will not resume work on
OL,16,Flegally aided crown court cases "until
OL,17,Fthe department shows the pragmatism
OL,18,Fand the urgency that's required to
OL,19,Fresolve the issue of crown court fees".
