OL,7,FCounsel in the region had already
OL,8,Fwithdrawn their services in some legal
OL,9,Faid-funded cases last year due to the
OL,10,Flong-running dispute with Stormont's
OL,11,FDepartment of Justice.
OL,13,FBarristers plan to increase their
OL,14,Faction from Monday by not
OL,15,Fparticipating in any current cases
OL,16,Fbefore the crown courts.
OL,18,FOf the 193 members of the Criminal Bar
OL,19,FAssociation (CBA) who voted on the
OL,20,Fproposal, 89% backed a full withdrawal
OL,21,Fof services.
