OL,7,FThe CBA says fees for legally aided
OL,8,Fcriminal work have not been increased
OL,9,Fsince 2005, making them worth just 50%
OL,10,Fof their original value.
OL,12,FStormont Justice minister Naomi Long
OL,13,Fhas committed to increasing their fee
OL,14,Frates by 16%.
