OL,7,FMr Lunny said he recognised that Ms
OL,8,FLong was in a "difficult position" as
OL,9,Fa result of funding cuts to the
OL,10,Fdepartment, but that "in the overall
OL,11,Fscheme of the Department of Justice's
OL,12,Fbudget and funds, a relatively small
OL,13,Famount of money is all that's required
OL,14,Fto resolve this long standing problem."
