OL,7,FHe told the Press Association: "We
OL,8,Fknow, for example that the data breach
OL,9,Fcase (compensation claim from PSNI
OL,10,Fofficers whose details were made
OL,11,Fpublic in a 2023 data breach), a
OL,12,Fconservative estimate as to how much
OL,13,Fthat will cost the Department of
OL,14,FJustice and the PSNI is something like
OL,15,F#119 million ` that's essentially the
