OL,7,F"So as to how the minister in the
OL,8,Fdepartment manage their money, that's
OL,9,Fa matter for them. But in overall
OL,10,Fterms what's required to fix this is a
OL,11,Frelatively small amount of money."
OL,13,FSir Brain Leveson's review of criminal
OL,14,Fcourts in England and Wales showed a
OL,15,Fbacklog of up to 80,000 cases, with
OL,16,Fnew trials listed as far in the future
OL,17,Fas 2030, a five-year wait from the
OL,18,Fpoint of charge.
