OL,7,FMr Lunny said the criminal justice
OL,8,Fsystem in Northern Ireland is headed
OL,9,Fthe same way if the problems are not
OL,10,Fresolved.
OL,12,F"In a way, the strike is a red
OL,13,Fherring. The real crisis is that
OL,14,Fbarristers and solicitors firms aren't
OL,15,Fdoing criminal work because the legal
OL,16,Faid rates are so poor," he said.
