OL,7,F"In England and Wales, even though the
OL,8,Flegal aid rates are much better than
OL,9,Fthey are here, they can't attract
OL,10,Fsufficient numbers of barristers
OL,11,Feither to do the defence work or the
OL,12,Fprosecution work, and that crisis that
OL,13,Fthey're having is where we will end up
OL,14,Fif the rates aren't improved and
OL,15,Fimproved significantly."
