OL,7,FHe added that young barristers in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland "are not interested
OL,9,Fin doing crown court work because the
OL,10,Fpay is so poor, so you have an ever
OL,11,Fdwindling cohort of older barristers
OL,12,Fdoing that work".
OL,14,FThe family of Natalie McNally, who
OL,15,Fdied after she was stabbed at her home
OL,16,Fin 2022, described the potential of
OL,17,Ffurther delays in her murder trial as
OL,18,Fa "kick in the teeth" when a judge
OL,19,Flast month cautioned the court may not
OL,20,Fbe able to proceed in January as
OL,21,Fplanned due to industrial action.
