OL,7,FMr Lunny said barristers "aren't
OL,8,Fblind" to the impact the strikes will
OL,9,Fhave on victims.
OL,11,F"Barristers who are practicing in the
OL,12,Fcrown court every day know exactly how
OL,13,Ftraumatic those cases can be," he said.
OL,15,F"It won't just have an impact on
OL,16,Fvictims, it will have an impact on
OL,17,Faccused persons. It will have an
OL,18,Fimpact on witnesses. It will have an
OL,19,Fimpact on jurors, people who are asked
OL,20,Fto serve on juries, so our members are
OL,21,Fvery aware of the impact it will have.
