OL,7,F"It's important to recognise that it
OL,8,Fwas very much a last resort step. It
OL,9,Fwas a step that was not lightly taken.
OL,11,F"As to how much of an impact it has,
OL,12,Fthat's very much in the hands of the
OL,13,Fdepartment.
OL,15,F"The department, if they want to deal
OL,16,Fwith this crisis ` and there is a
OL,17,Fcrisis in the criminal justice system
OL,18,Faside from this strike ` there is a
OL,19,Fcrisis in the system that the
OL,20,Fdepartment aren't showing any urgency
OL,21,Fin attempting to tackle."
