OL,7,FWhen industrial action was announced,
OL,8,FMs Long accused barristers of seeking
OL,9,Fto "leverage further trauma and stress
OL,10,Fon victims" and said she wasn't
OL,11,Fconfident "the CBA is committed to
OL,12,Fmeaningful engagement".
OL,14,FMr Lunny said Northern Ireland's Lady
OL,15,FChief Justice Dame Siobhan Keegan
OL,16,Fadvised in November that the CBA and
OL,17,Fdepartment engage with a specialist
OL,18,Fmediator, to which the barristers
OL,19,Faccepted and the department declined.
