OL,7,F"We don't know their reasons, because
OL,8,Fwe've never seen the letter that they
OL,9,Fwrote to the Lady Chief Justice, but
OL,10,Fwe have always been and we remain
OL,11,Fwilling, ready to mediate with the
OL,12,Fdepartment if they change their mind,"
OL,13,Fhe said.
OL,15,FThe Justice minister said she is
OL,16,F"profoundly disappointed and
OL,17,Ffrustrated" by the industrial action,
OL,18,Fwhich she described as "not
OL,19,Fjustifiable or necessary".
