OL,7,FMs Long said the Bar agreed to a road-
OL,8,Fmap as part of a working group chaired
OL,9,Fby His Honour Judge Tom Burgess.
OL,11,F"The road-map provided direction on
OL,12,Fall the areas the CBA has indicated
OL,13,Fmust be addressed to enable members
OL,14,Freturn to full service delivery," she
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"Yet, just a few days later, the CBA
OL,18,Fannounced a complete withdrawal of
OL,19,Fservices."
