OL,7,FShe added: "Given Judge Burgess'
OL,8,Funique insight into the discussions
OL,9,Fwithin the working group to date, I
OL,10,Fplace significant weight on his
OL,11,Fcontinuing view that without
OL,12,Fdeveloping that evidence there can be
OL,13,Fno basis for determining what is
OL,14,Fproper and reasonable remuneration,
OL,15,Fand that any 'mediation process will
OL,16,Ffind itself in exactly the same
